<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>سُورَةُ العاديات<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c3">{إِنَّ الْإِنْسَانَ لِرَبِّهِ لَكَنُودٌ , وَإِنَّهُ عَلَى ذَلِكَ لَشَهِيدٌ , وَإِنَّهُ لِحُبِّ الْخَيْرِ لَشَدِيدٌ}</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص١٧٦:</span> قَالَ مُجَاهِدٌ: الكَنُودُ: الكَفُورُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">يُقَالُ:</span> <span class="c3">{فَأَثَرْنَ بِهِ نَقْعًا}</span>: رَفَعْنَا بِهِ غُبَارًا<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c3">{لِحُبِّ الخَيْرِ}</span>: مِنْ أَجْلِ حُبِّ الخَيْرِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c3">{لَشَدِيدٌ}</span>: لَبَخِيلٌ،<span class="c5"> وَيُقَالُ لِلْبَخِيلِ:</span> شَدِيدٌ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c3">{حُصِّلَ}</span>: مُيِّزَ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) [العاديات: ٦ - ٨]</p> </div>